13 WHEREAS, the phenomenal performance of the team is a clear indication of the outstanding
14 athletic ability, dedication, hard work, and unity of purpose and spirit of each member of the
15 team; and
16 WHEREAS, this magnificent team performed with precision during the season and earned
17 its well-deserved reputation for high standards of athletic achievement, the quality of its play,
18 and the stiff competition it presented to its opponents.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
20 congratulate the Toombs County High School football team for winning the 2024 GHSA
21 Class A Division 1 State Football Championship and extend best wishes for continued
22 success.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
24 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Toombs
25 County High School football team.
